 font-size:11pt">also </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">serves a broader public interest in deterring abuse of po</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">wer</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">.</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">Application of the residence test</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold"> to LASPO</span></p><ol start="3" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 32.17pt; padding-left:3.83pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Within our specialist area, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">those who fall foul of </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">t</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">he proposed residence test will </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">be </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">exclude</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">d</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> from accessing legal aid </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">under the following provisions of the Legal Aid, Sentencing and Punishment of </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Offenders’ Act (LASPO)</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> Schedule 1 Part 1:</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="background-c